		<div id="post_message_1299488">
                  
                  As jades has said NO SORCEROR content or update till next patch. We are the hardest as we are the most screwed up and most effort to change our abilities or add to them has been met with coding failure so far.<br />
<br />
As for the character customization changes, i really do not care if they will indeed boost up performance for the benefit of using higher configuration settings for the overal environment detail. As the developers ahd stated these changes had to be done for both performance and the use of helmets so that ears or jaws would not stick out from helmets.<br />
<br />
Riftway system is ok for the pve aspect and i think i like it more epsecially if we get the flying mount Still hope tha t the end quest is not to kill the apw dragon as it has been rumoured cause that would simly freak me off and cancell right away). The one thing i really did not like and would yet beg J<b><font size="5">ades to validate</font></b> for me is the fact that the developers have made a coding error by forcing anyone who casts to get dismounted. You see you cannot use invi when you are on a horse so you cannot run about invisible on your mount.<br />
<br />
It says also that ALL attuning crystals are purchasable from the exotic vendor guy, hope this includes then attuning crystals of health which ar as rare as protection crystals.... <br />
The rest of the resonating crystals should be drops from mobs according to people.<br />
<br />
The real reason that keep me still in this game ( i have cancelled twice so far only to revoke it because of jades words) is the fact that after at least 8 months of having totally fucke up with the sorceror as a class in pvp i MIGHT still get some revamp. I lalso MIGHT still not be a 2 buff mage in raids with no other presence other than that of a &quot;cowering&quot; dpser who will give up his real dps power for the sake of health armour so as not to die so often and pray that aggro management from MT will keep him alive.<br />
<br />
Personally jades i expect developers to give word within a month of what is going to happen to sorcerors in the future, pvp or pve. I have not  pvped on sorceror intensely anyway for over 8 months other than the guild duels we hold so often to know the other classes in pvp. But as even emilia has said fuck pvp &quot;for now&quot;. No word even on the pve aspects other than those forms which are not so important in my opinion they way they have been designed.<br />
<br />
I have been criticised on boards for my &quot;rough&quot; posts on how fucked up we are as a class, how screwed up developers and coding are and yet i see people cancelling for reasons other than gameplay. <br />
<br />
And one more observation, which i hope will not be taken wrongly as people here so often do. I have seen developers posting quite so often on other class boards but never here. That proves to me how they are cowering for what they have to done to this class. <br />
<br />
So back to test server to see things more indepth, and chill out. We are the best paying (not paid) beta testers in the history of online mmorpgs.
                  
