                  Well i also look at the bright/lame side of things..... I go everywhere around hunting sorcerors psi paladins dks and warriors form the other enemy guilds that are on our kos list and the bard simply rocks there. I even tried to psychologically analyze this behaviour of mine but what the hell , i got an easy answer... it is addictive and it is fun. There is nothing else to do right now other than hunt in island of madness or harvest or do endless apw..... even now i get bored by that. <br />
