As i said it is anticipation of the things to come that keeps me in this game apart from the awesome and jaw-dropping graphics of this game. All my greek friends just fled the game a long time ago and went back to wow ( bleah bleah). <br />
<br />
I had a look at warhammer and it seems a bit wowish to me. Not bad graphics but basic and very cartoonlike. A lot of the changes that i saw on the test server , i finally resolved, are indeed AWESOME ..... no more attuning of health stuoid farming, no more lining up for domination on island of madness for crystals, no more decon failure ( i could seriously grasp silius by the neck and stranggle him over and over again for that painful shit of decon failure). <br />
<br />
But finally and above all no matter how i whine and no matter how many times i have cancelled subscription i finally decided that the guild i am in on sartok (law) is an awesome guild wiht really nice people, there is still some basic pvp going on that keeps interest alive and FINALLY ( i like repeating myself sometimes) it is ANTICIPATION for the things to come. <br />
<br />
I know jades has been silent for quite some time. I learnt from other class leads the sad truth about class leads being ignored invariably by developers, even them being in the dark about upcoming changes, but i am a stubborn mule asshole myself who will stick around with the last hope of seeing  the disaster or revolution of sorcerors. I will stay for the last straw and whine and whine. In any case we expect the changes to come in 2 month..... no game ahead in those 2 months for me<br />
